'''number_towns''' is a variable of Openttd.cfg file:

Sets the frequency of towns created on a new map.

0 = very low<br>
1 = low<br>
2 = normal<br>
3 = high<br>
4 = custom<br>

The custom setting is modified by the [[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Custom town number]] setting in the <nowiki>[game_creation]</nowiki> section.

<pre>
[difficulty]
number_towns = 2
</pre>

'''Valid options:''' [ 0 | 1 | 2 | 3 | 4 ]

'''Default:''' 2


